@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ryqxto(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.16 * tmp + 0.91) * v1))
    v1 = v1
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.44) * (v0 + 0.78 + v2 + 0.02)) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.69) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.48)))
    data[tid] = v0
